Hey!

9
00:02:14,380 --> 00:02:15,130
Why are you here?

10
00:02:15,430 --> 00:02:16,200
Come in!

11
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:18,310
Come.

12
00:02:18,430 --> 00:02:19,000
Come to my room.

13
00:02:25,470 --> 00:02:25,870
Here.

14
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,120
Have some water.

15
00:02:30,750 --> 00:02:32,350
You didn't answer my calls,

16
00:02:32,660 --> 00:02:34,290
