17
00:02:36,030 --> 00:02:37,079
I'm a light sleeper.

18
00:02:37,430 --> 00:02:38,320
My phone was muted.

19
00:02:39,030 --> 00:02:39,710
What's up?

20
00:02:40,910 --> 00:02:41,980
Kai wants to

21
00:02:42,750 --> 00:02:44,120
treat us to a seafood feast.

22
00:02:44,470 --> 00:02:45,400
He repeatedly

23
00:02:45,420 --> 00:02:46,950
insisted that I invite you.

24
00:02:50,980 --> 00:02:52,380
Why are you all shy?

25
00:02:57,590 --> 00:02:58,800
Who's the girl at the door?

26
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,120
A friend's relative.

27
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:02,280
She's visiting.

28
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:03,590
She's staying here for a few days.

29
00:03:05,560 --> 00:03:06,840
Let's get her to join us tonight.

30
00:03:06,920 --> 00:03:07,800
Don't leave her out.

31
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:09,400
Sure.

32
00:03:21,320 --> 00:03:21,920
Miss.

33
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:25,079
I'll get going.

34
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:28,079
What big eyes.

35
00:03:39,720 --> 00:03:40,630
Stop cooking.

36
00:03:40,750 --> 00:03:41,800
Eat out with me later.

37
00:03:44,470 --> 00:03:45,840
Eat out with you?

38
00:03:46,750 --> 00:03:47,310
Why?

39
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:49,280
Someone's treating.

40
00:03:49,550 --> 00:03:50,280
You can join.

41
00:03:51,079 --> 00:03:51,840
It's a free meal.

42
00:03:52,190 --> 00:03:53,190
Don't ask so many questions.

43
00:03:55,590 --> 00:03:56,870
That woman who just came?

44
00:03:59,190 --> 00:03:59,680
No thanks.

45
00:04:00,420 --> 00:04:01,120
What did she do to you?

46
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:03,480
I got bad vibes from her,

47
00:04:03,820 --> 00:04:05,570
as if she came from hell.

48
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:06,470
Ominous.

49
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:08,280
She didn't provoke you.

50
00:04:09,030 --> 00:04:10,260
Why are you so mean?

51
00:04:10,710 --> 00:04:11,560
That's

52
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:12,560
my instinct.

53
00:04:12,750 --> 00:04:13,800
You always hang out with

54
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:14,350
those people.

55
00:04:14,370 --> 00:04:15,330
You're immune to those vibes.

56
00:04:15,710 --> 00:04:17,600
So vile at a young age.

57
00:04:17,630 --> 00:04:18,720
Watch out for karma.

58
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:19,829
Just you wait.

59
00:04:30,870 --> 00:04:31,510
Why did

60
00:04:31,550 --> 00:04:32,700
your mom buy you this toy?

61
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:36,390
Do you know who he is?

62
00:04:37,310 --> 00:04:37,920
No.

63
00:04:39,300 --> 00:04:40,390
His name is Sisyphus.

64
00:04:40,620 --> 00:04:42,120
Who is Sisyphus?

65
00:04:42,550 --> 00:04:43,920
A mythical figure

66
00:04:43,950 --> 00:04:45,310
in ancient Greek.

67
00:04:46,080 --> 00:04:47,000
He's unlucky.

68
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:48,510
He offended Zeus.

69
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:51,070
Who is Zeus?

70
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:54,560
Zeus was... his boss.

71
00:04:55,930 --> 00:04:57,430
So, Zeus punished him

72
00:04:57,450 --> 00:04:58,330
to push a boulder

73
00:04:58,360 --> 00:04:59,360
to the top of the mountain.

74
00:04:59,630 --> 00:05:00,560
When he got to the peak,

75
00:05:00,830 --> 00:05:01,840
the boulder was too heavy

76
00:05:02,070 --> 00:05:02,950
that it rolled down.

77
00:05:03,270 --> 00:05:04,040
After that,

78
00:05:04,510 --> 00:05:05,360
he went down the mountain

79
00:05:05,630 --> 00:05:06,560
to push it up again.

80
00:05:06,750 --> 00:05:08,190
Again and again,

81
00:05:08,750 --> 00:05:10,160
day after day,

82
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:12,190
year after year,

83
00:05:12,530 --> 00:05:13,480
forever and ever.

84
00:05:14,130 --> 00:05:15,890
Dad, you're Sisyphus.

85
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:19,720
What do you mean?

86
00:05:21,850 --> 00:05:22,800
When you have to catch bad guys,

87
00:05:22,830 --> 00:05:24,120
you don't come home, right?

88
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:25,630
Basically.

89
00:05:27,190 --> 00:05:28,000
In the end,

90
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:29,270
you can't catch them,

91
00:05:29,270 --> 00:05:31,120
and you've to keep going after them,

92
00:05:31,200 --> 00:05:32,650
again and again,

93
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:34,120
repeating the same thing.

94
00:05:35,010 --> 00:05:35,750
Aren't you

95
00:05:35,750 --> 00:05:37,070
just like Sisyphus?

96
00:05:50,950 --> 00:05:51,430
Come in.

97
00:05:52,580 --> 00:05:53,040
Director Jiang.

98
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:55,600
Captain Peng.

99
00:05:58,430 --> 00:05:59,780
Someone's suing you, you know?

100
00:06:00,330 --> 00:06:00,920
Who?

101
00:06:01,830 --> 00:06:03,160
Liu Liang, someone related to

102
00:06:03,310 --> 00:06:04,680
the victim of the 11/03 case.

103
00:06:04,970 --> 00:06:05,570
For what?

104
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:08,760
You promised to solve

105
00:06:09,190 --> 00:06:09,950
the case.

106
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:11,830
The two old folks

107
00:06:12,240 --> 00:06:13,010
are seriously ill

108
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:13,950
with no tomorrow.

109
00:06:14,970 --> 00:06:15,830
And you still

110
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,000
haven't accounted

111
00:06:18,580 --> 00:06:19,610
for their daughter.

112
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:21,680
So,

113
00:06:22,270 --> 00:06:23,310
their request is

114
00:06:23,310 --> 00:06:25,040
for you to give them closure

115
00:06:25,890 --> 00:06:26,690
before they pass.

116
00:06:30,970 --> 00:06:31,760
Then...

117
00:06:32,870 --> 00:06:33,600
How can I do that?

118
00:06:34,430 --> 00:06:35,240
Get removed from my post?

119
00:06:35,650 --> 00:06:37,010
You were already transferred away.

120
00:06:37,390 --> 00:06:38,470
Where else can you go?

121
00:06:38,760 --> 00:06:39,680
Guard the gates?

122
00:06:40,810 --> 00:06:41,930
Tell me what you think.

123
00:06:46,640 --> 00:06:47,830
I was in charge of

124
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:49,630
the 11/03 case.

125
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:53,390
What

126
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:54,920
those criminals think

127
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:56,520
and how they operate...

128
00:06:58,270 --> 00:06:59,190
I know it best.

129
00:07:01,310 --> 00:07:02,360
Forget about objective reasons.

130
00:07:03,730 --> 00:07:04,760
I failed to catch them.

131
00:07:05,830 --> 00:07:06,830
I fully accept

132
00:07:08,190 --> 00:07:09,040
being sued

133
00:07:09,220 --> 00:07:10,190
for inaction.

134
00:07:11,350 --> 00:07:12,380
I was kicked out of the Special Task Force.

135
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:13,510
That's...

136
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:15,870
my due punishment too.

137
00:07:18,430 --> 00:07:19,240
Don't beat around the bush.

138
00:07:19,390 --> 00:07:20,830
Just say what you think.

139
00:07:21,630 --> 00:07:22,950
Tell me everything you think.

140
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:23,870
Director Jiang.

141
00:07:26,310 --> 00:07:27,160
I couldn't solve it.

142
00:07:29,870 --> 00:07:30,830
I'm upset too.

143
00:07:31,910 --> 00:07:33,140
What worries me most now

144
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:35,190
is that those criminals

145
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,310
are very cruel.

146
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:39,240
From the info we have on them,

147
00:07:40,310 --> 00:07:41,830
before they're brought to justice,

148
00:07:42,230 --> 00:07:43,300
they'll keep at it.

149
00:07:44,110 --> 00:07:44,680
This...

150
00:07:45,630 --> 00:07:46,190
will put

151
00:07:46,190 --> 00:07:47,420
our society in peril.

152
00:07:52,159 --> 00:07:53,470
The 11/03 case

153
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:55,080
is really complicated.

154
00:07:55,510 --> 00:07:56,480
I just took office.

155
00:07:56,950 --> 00:07:57,630
So far,

156
00:07:58,120 --> 00:07:59,390
we haven't found a breakthrough.

157
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:00,510
To be honest,

158
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:01,870
everyone is

159
