very anxious.

160
00:08:04,830 --> 00:08:06,950
Just say what you want.

161
00:08:07,870 --> 00:08:08,360
Okay.

162
00:08:10,140 --> 00:08:10,950
Transfer me back.

163
00:08:14,510 --> 00:08:15,000
That's all?

164
00:08:15,870 --> 00:08:16,310
No.

165
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:19,560
Transfer your buddies

166
00:08:19,710 --> 00:08:21,050
back too, right?

167
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,240
They know the details.

168
00:08:22,830 --> 00:08:23,480
Saves time.

169
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:28,630
Tell me.

170
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:30,870
How confident are you?

171
00:08:32,030 --> 00:08:32,630
100%.

172
00:08:35,030 --> 00:08:36,070
I've heard that too many times.

173
00:08:40,120 --> 00:08:40,880
I trust you.

174
00:08:47,120 --> 00:08:47,550
Thank you.

175
00:09:51,670 --> 00:09:52,510
You're late!

176
00:09:52,530 --> 00:09:53,750
I'm sorry I'm late.

177
00:09:53,770 --> 00:09:54,400
Forgive me.

178
00:09:54,430 --> 00:09:55,640
Drink as punishment.

179
00:09:55,670 --> 00:09:56,200
Sure.

180
00:09:56,200 --> 00:09:57,430
Sorry, forgive me.

181
00:09:59,240 --> 00:09:59,750
Kai.

182
00:10:00,410 --> 00:10:01,360
Where should I sit?

183
00:10:01,980 --> 00:10:02,940
Sit next to me.

184
00:10:03,190 --> 00:10:04,240
I reserved the spot for you.

185
00:10:06,030 --> 00:10:07,420
Since I was late, I'll drink as punishment.

186
00:10:07,930 --> 00:10:08,600
Sure.

187
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,440
Let me drink with you.

188
00:10:11,440 --> 00:10:11,870
Here.

189
00:10:20,320 --> 00:10:21,510
I'm really sorry.

190
00:10:22,030 --> 00:10:22,480
I only

191
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:24,030
have two hours today.

192
00:10:24,420 --> 00:10:25,610
I have to go to work later.

193
00:10:26,400 --> 00:10:27,370
Is that a problem?

194
00:10:27,630 --> 00:10:28,150
You know what,

195
00:10:28,750 --> 00:10:29,550
my buddy will

196
00:10:29,810 --> 00:10:30,770
call your manager

197
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:31,550
to ask for leave.

198
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:33,000
It's that Liu, right?

199
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:33,600
Well...

200
00:10:33,790 --> 00:10:34,840
I really can't.

201
00:10:34,840 --> 00:10:35,240
I...

202
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:36,440
I have to make money.

203
00:10:37,590 --> 00:10:38,750
How much can you make in a day?

204
00:10:38,750 --> 00:10:39,270
Share it with me.

205
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:40,910
How rude are you?

206
00:10:41,450 --> 00:10:42,520
That's private.

207
00:10:42,550 --> 00:10:43,480
I'll keep the change.

208
00:10:44,060 --> 00:10:45,060
This is for you, okay?

209
00:10:45,580 --> 00:10:46,690
That's too much.

210
00:10:46,760 --> 00:10:48,580
What's too much? Take it. He's loaded.

211
00:10:49,320 --> 00:10:50,380
Don't go to work tonight.

212
00:10:50,700 --> 00:10:51,670
Just hang out with us.

213
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:52,270
Okay.

214
00:10:52,910 --> 00:10:53,550
Thank you.

215
00:10:54,090 --> 00:10:54,660
Treat yourself.

216
00:10:58,630 --> 00:10:59,030
Here.

217
00:10:59,030 --> 00:10:59,600
Thank you.

218
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:01,080
Let me fill your glass.

219
00:11:02,390 --> 00:11:03,810
Where is that girl?

220
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:05,000
Why isn't she here?

221
00:11:05,670 --> 00:11:06,240
Her?

222
00:11:06,450 --> 00:11:07,760
She... She is immature

223
00:11:07,790 --> 00:11:08,440
and stubborn.

224
00:11:08,790 --> 00:11:09,690
She'll just spoil the mood.

225
00:11:09,720 --> 00:11:10,620
She can't drink too.

226
00:11:10,670 --> 00:11:11,630
I'll drink with you. Come on.

227
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:14,510
