228
00:11:14,820 --> 00:11:15,580
What a waste.

229
00:11:16,550 --> 00:11:17,000
Yeah.

230
00:11:17,870 --> 00:11:18,750
Oh well,

231
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:20,240
