232
00:11:20,510 --> 00:11:21,390
Call her and tell her

233
00:11:21,510 --> 00:11:22,150
to get here.

234
00:11:22,390 --> 00:11:24,030
Yeah? The more, the merrier.

235
00:11:32,550 --> 00:11:32,960
Here.

236
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:34,510
After the call,

237
00:11:35,080 --> 00:11:35,720
have this.

238
00:11:35,910 --> 00:11:37,130
Here, have this.

239
00:11:37,340 --> 00:11:38,000
Thank you.

240
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:41,960
No one answered.

241
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:43,640
It's okay. Ignore her.

242
00:11:43,670 --> 00:11:44,360
Let's enjoy ourselves.

243
00:11:46,150 --> 00:11:47,080
It's not far.

244
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:48,550
Why don't you go get her?

245
00:11:48,670 --> 00:11:49,080
Okay.

246
00:11:50,060 --> 00:11:51,380
The food won't be good if you take it back.

247
00:11:51,600 --> 00:11:52,480
That's good. Leave some for me.

248
00:11:52,520 --> 00:11:53,080
Okay.

249
00:11:54,000 --> 00:11:54,840
Come on. Cheers.

250
00:11:58,550 --> 00:11:59,960
You really care a lot

251
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:01,010
about that girl.

252
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:03,270
Come, let's drink.

253
00:12:03,270 --> 00:12:03,910
Come on.

254
00:12:04,440 --> 00:12:04,870
Sir.

255
00:12:06,030 --> 00:12:07,840
These two bosses are in the electricity business.

256
00:12:07,910 --> 00:12:08,910
What do you do?

257
00:12:10,480 --> 00:12:11,600
I'm in publishing.

258
00:12:11,910 --> 00:12:12,510
Publishing?

259
00:12:13,350 --> 00:12:14,330
Can't you tell?

260
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:17,320
I specialize in poetry.

261
00:12:18,790 --> 00:12:20,050
Is it profitable?

262
00:12:20,910 --> 00:12:21,630
Extremely.

263
00:12:21,680 --> 00:12:22,290
Really?

264
00:12:22,320 --> 00:12:23,490
Like "Three Hundred Tang Poems."

265
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:26,120
You're amazing!

266
00:12:27,030 --> 00:12:28,300
