267
00:12:28,570 --> 00:12:29,780
The beauty rolls up the curtain.

268
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:32,790
No trace of anyone for thousands of miles.

269
00:12:34,030 --> 00:12:34,510
Right?

270
00:12:35,750 --> 00:12:37,960
The apes on both shores can't stop crying.

271
00:12:38,960 --> 00:12:39,320
Right?

272
00:12:39,470 --> 00:12:40,920
