289
00:13:38,520 --> 00:13:39,290
Listen to me.

290
00:13:39,320 --> 00:13:40,410
It's just a meal.

291
00:13:40,440 --> 00:13:41,360
Stop following me.

292
00:13:41,360 --> 00:13:42,510
I said I'm not going.

293
00:13:42,510 --> 00:13:43,760
I need to find a job.

294
00:13:43,790 --> 00:13:44,520
Look at you.

295
00:13:44,550 --> 00:13:45,670
What's wrong with a meal?

296
00:13:58,720 --> 00:13:59,910
I told you she wouldn't come.

297
00:14:02,150 --> 00:14:03,420
Come on, let's drink.

298
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:05,620
Qiu Feng, you're so sensible.

299
00:14:06,960 --> 00:14:07,910
Have one with me too.

300
00:14:13,870 --> 00:14:14,920
You haven't told me

301
00:14:15,720 --> 00:14:17,120
