343
00:16:12,720 --> 00:16:15,320
Let me go look for her!

344
00:16:31,160 --> 00:16:32,410
Hubby.

345
00:16:32,670 --> 00:16:36,510
I lost my precious daughter.

346
00:16:40,750 --> 00:16:43,390
Where can I find her?

347
00:16:43,390 --> 00:16:45,840
What should I do?

348
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:33,030
Don't just smile.

349
00:17:33,030 --> 00:17:33,790
Press the elevator.

350
00:17:35,060 --> 00:17:35,440
Let's go.

351
00:17:35,480 --> 00:17:35,960
Come on.

352
00:17:38,960 --> 00:17:39,440
Sir.

353
00:17:51,150 --> 00:17:51,590
Here.

354
00:17:52,480 --> 00:17:54,850
Let me pour you another glass.

355
00:17:55,200 --> 00:17:56,400
I can't drink anymore.

356
00:17:56,550 --> 00:17:57,510
I'll get drunk.

357
00:17:57,790 --> 00:17:58,920
Then just sleep here.

358
00:17:59,270 --> 00:18:00,640
We have beds here.

359
00:18:00,750 --> 00:18:01,400
I'll drink with you.

360
00:18:02,010 --> 00:18:02,550
Bottoms up.

361
00:18:08,070 --> 00:18:09,070
Bottoms up!

362
00:18:09,270 --> 00:18:10,270
I've emptied mine.

363
00:18:11,110 --> 00:18:12,160
I really can't drink anymore.

364
00:18:12,160 --> 00:18:12,920
Come on.

365
00:18:13,030 --> 00:18:13,510
Come on.

366
00:18:13,640 --> 00:18:14,110
I'll drink

367
00:18:14,240 --> 00:18:14,920
another with you.

368
00:18:15,480 --> 00:18:15,920
Okay?

369
00:18:16,230 --> 00:18:16,680
Here.

370
00:18:22,280 --> 00:18:23,750
