371
00:18:23,920 --> 00:18:24,550
No.

372
00:18:25,350 --> 00:18:26,640
This is my own hair.

373
00:18:26,920 --> 00:18:27,710
Really?

374
00:18:28,240 --> 00:18:28,750
Look.

375
00:19:35,000 --> 00:19:35,850
What do you want?

376
00:19:36,480 --> 00:19:37,070
Let me go.

377
00:19:37,920 --> 00:19:38,550
Let me go.

378
00:19:39,060 --> 00:19:40,030
Help!

379
00:19:54,520 --> 00:19:55,350
No one can hear you

380
00:19:55,410 --> 00:19:57,040
through these walls.

381
00:20:03,240 --> 00:20:04,350
Call that girl.

382
00:20:05,550 --> 00:20:06,200
Get her here.

383
00:20:09,260 --> 00:20:10,790
We're not on good terms.

384
00:20:11,600 --> 00:20:12,850
She wouldn't agree.

385
00:20:25,170 --> 00:20:25,960
Not on good terms?

386
00:20:27,430 --> 00:20:28,230
Not on good terms?

387
00:20:34,110 --> 00:20:34,680
I think...

388
00:20:37,310 --> 00:20:38,440
you like me the most.

389
00:20:40,540 --> 00:20:42,350
Because I'm the gentlest one.

390
00:20:49,400 --> 00:20:50,550
Don't provoke him.

391
00:20:51,480 --> 00:20:52,510
If you do...

392
00:20:57,480 --> 00:20:58,400
you'll know what hell is.

393
00:21:07,550 --> 00:21:08,110
Call her.

394
00:21:16,200 --> 00:21:16,720
Press the number.

395
00:21:53,210 --> 00:21:54,380
No one answered.

396
00:21:59,510 --> 00:22:00,000
Shun.

397
00:22:04,240 --> 00:22:05,480
She sure is beautiful.

398
00:22:07,310 --> 00:22:08,270
Did I call you here to admire her?

399
00:22:26,460 --> 00:22:27,660
Since no one answered, let's kill her.

400
00:22:43,320 --> 00:22:45,680
Looks like this rope is quite firm.

401
00:23:10,870 --> 00:23:12,060
That girl saw me.

402
00:23:13,110 --> 00:23:14,270
We can't let her live.

403
00:23:16,270 --> 00:23:17,200
Aren't these her house keys?

404
00:23:17,920 --> 00:23:18,640
I'll just go get her

405
00:23:18,640 --> 00:23:19,270
here now.

406
00:23:20,480 --> 00:23:21,750
It's late at night.

407
00:23:23,000 --> 00:23:23,590
Tomorrow.

408
00:23:24,590 --> 00:23:25,640
Find a time tomorrow.

409
00:23:30,150 --> 00:23:31,450
Qiu Feng got drunk last night

410
00:23:31,480 --> 00:23:32,350
and is sleeping in my house.

411
00:23:32,370 --> 00:23:33,280
I need to go out.

412
00:23:33,310 --> 00:23:34,000
Get her out.

413
00:23:34,750 --> 00:23:35,310
If she's drunk,

414
00:23:35,330 --> 00:23:36,620
just get her out yourself.

415
00:23:36,790 --> 00:23:37,790
She has her keys.

416
00:23:38,310 --> 00:23:39,160
You don't need me.

417
00:23:39,360 --> 00:23:40,720
If I could do it alone,

418
00:23:40,720 --> 00:23:41,750
why'd I ask you?

419
00:23:42,030 --> 00:23:43,370
It's not easy for me to find a job.

420
00:23:43,400 --> 00:23:44,790
If I leave now,

421
00:23:44,810 --> 00:23:45,860
I'll lose my job.

422
00:23:47,000 --> 00:23:47,720
Are you serious?

423
00:23:47,720 --> 00:23:49,310
Why're you so cold-blooded?

424
00:23:50,580 --> 00:23:52,060
I just live with her,

425
00:23:52,550 --> 00:23:53,790
nothing else.

426
00:24:07,030 --> 00:24:07,400
Here.

427
00:24:08,240 --> 00:24:09,000
Take this call.

428
00:24:09,770 --> 00:24:10,420
It's Qiu Feng!

429
00:24:15,780 --> 00:24:16,430
What is it?

430
00:24:26,070 --> 00:24:26,750
Zhen Zhen.

431
00:24:28,350 --> 00:24:29,270
Do a friend a favor.

432
00:24:30,030 --> 00:24:31,310
Come and pick me up.

433
00:24:31,640 --> 00:24:32,840
You're my friend now?

434
00:24:33,420 --> 00:24:34,300
We're not friends.

435
00:24:34,330 --> 00:24:35,000
Just get

436
00:24:35,020 --> 00:24:36,090
one of your boyfriends to help you.

437
00:25:18,030 --> 00:25:18,880
Tell me.

438
00:25:22,150 --> 00:25:23,910
Why doesn't she care about you?

439
00:25:47,510 --> 00:25:48,510
Let me teach you.

440
00:25:54,180 --> 00:25:55,390
I'll teach you.

441
00:25:57,650 --> 00:25:59,670
Then she'll answer your call.

442
00:26:09,670 --> 00:26:10,760
Do you remember...

443
00:26:13,040 --> 00:26:15,130
what we talked about when we were dancing?

444
00:26:17,170 --> 00:26:17,900
I don't remember.

445
00:26:18,680 --> 00:26:19,890
I asked you

446
00:26:21,140 --> 00:26:23,470
if you like your current job.

447
00:26:25,460 --> 00:26:26,170
No, I don't.

448
00:26:29,440 --> 00:26:30,680
Then why

449
00:26:31,370 --> 00:26:33,040
are you in this business?

450
00:26:36,790 --> 00:26:37,790
It's quick.

451
00:26:39,410 --> 00:26:42,450
Clocking in for work is so tough.

452
00:26:46,220 --> 00:26:47,390
Clocking in for work...

453
00:26:50,130 --> 00:26:51,370
is so tough.

454
00:27:07,010 --> 00:27:07,490
Where's she?

455
00:27:16,400 --> 00:27:17,750
I told you I'm needed for this job.

456
00:27:20,230 --> 00:27:21,040
Sit down and rest.

457
00:27:21,920 --> 00:27:22,620
It's air-conditioned.

458
00:27:27,550 --> 00:27:29,000
I'm putting up the recruitment notices.

459
00:27:30,400 --> 00:27:31,470
Really? How many came?

460
00:27:32,930 --> 00:27:34,040
Not many places left then?

461
00:27:38,340 --> 00:27:39,340
Five left?

462
00:27:44,590 --> 00:27:45,670
Five left!

463
00:28:11,830 --> 00:28:12,870
You're dressed lightly.

464
00:28:37,910 --> 00:28:39,030
Call your dad.

465
00:28:40,560 --> 00:28:41,990
Ask him to transfer some money to your card.

466
00:28:43,160 --> 00:28:43,990
You said

467
00:28:44,590 --> 00:28:45,830
you didn't give much money to your family,

468
00:28:46,170 --> 00:28:46,680
right?

469
00:28:47,020 --> 00:28:47,630
How about this?

470
00:28:48,750 --> 00:28:49,510
Ask for 20,000 first.

471
00:28:50,140 --> 00:28:50,550
Come on.

472
00:28:53,120 --> 00:28:53,680
Read it.

473
00:28:58,230 --> 00:28:58,990
My friend...

474
00:29:00,190 --> 00:29:01,190
Do business...

475
00:29:02,290 --> 00:29:02,880
Profit...

476
00:29:05,160 --> 00:29:06,030
Read it properly.

477
00:29:06,150 --> 00:29:07,220
Stop crying.

478
00:29:15,530 --> 00:29:16,290
A friend of mine

479
00:29:17,790 --> 00:29:18,880
wants to do business with me.

480
00:29:19,840 --> 00:29:21,550
It yields 30% profit.

481
00:29:22,800 --> 00:29:23,920
Transfer me 20,000 yuan.

482
00:29:24,090 --> 00:29:24,890
Memorized it?

483
00:29:34,190 --> 00:29:35,840
Here, call him now.

484
00:29:55,620 --> 00:29:56,050
Hello?

485
00:29:57,430 --> 00:29:58,110
Dad.

486
00:29:59,160 --> 00:30:00,440
Transfer me 20,000 yuan.

487
00:30:01,710 --> 00:30:03,670
A friend of mine wants to do business with me.

488
00:30:04,670 --> 00:30:06,160
It yields 30% profit.

489
00:30:06,740 --> 00:30:07,400
You sent us

490
00:30:07,400 --> 00:30:08,720
13,000 in total.

491
00:30:08,770 --> 00:30:09,810
Your mom had an operation...

492
00:30:23,320 --> 00:30:24,190
Didn't you say

493
00:30:25,510 --> 00:30:26,510
you didn't send much money

494
00:30:26,530 --> 00:30:27,420
to your family?

495
00:30:32,590 --> 00:30:33,470
It's hot!

496
00:30:51,960 --> 00:30:53,880
Hey, do you have anything cold?

497
00:30:54,020 --> 00:30:54,830
There's ice cream.

498
00:30:55,350 --> 00:30:56,590
Ice cream's too sweet.

499
00:30:56,970 --> 00:30:58,100
How about this?

500
00:30:58,560 --> 00:30:59,350
Buy a bottle of water

501
00:30:59,350 --> 00:31:00,310
and I'll get you some ice.

502
00:31:00,710 --> 00:31:01,270
Sure.

503
00:31:02,450 --> 00:31:03,170
Coming right up.

504
00:31:05,200 --> 00:31:05,880
You can keep the water;

505
00:31:06,070 --> 00:31:07,070
I'll just take the ice.

506
00:32:16,360 --> 00:32:17,880
Have you been looking for me?

507
00:32:56,740 --> 00:32:57,200
Peng.

508
00:32:57,220 --> 00:32:57,660
Hey.

509
00:32:58,420 --> 00:32:59,040
Give me

510
00:32:59,090 --> 00:33:00,160
three vegetarian, three meat.

511
00:33:00,190 --> 00:33:00,720
Takeaway.

512
00:33:00,720 --> 00:33:01,160
Okay.

513
00:33:01,610 --> 00:33:02,040
Careful.

514
00:33:05,310 --> 00:33:05,960
Are you busy?

515
00:33:06,750 --> 00:33:07,310
Peng?

516
00:33:07,680 --> 00:33:08,510
How rare.

517
00:33:09,320 --> 00:33:10,480
I came to the morning market for buns.

518
00:33:10,510 --> 00:33:11,270
What's so rare?

519
00:33:12,620 --> 00:33:13,290
Peng, you're here.

520
00:33:13,840 --> 00:33:14,880
How's your mom doing?

521
00:33:15,160 --> 00:33:15,790
Report!

522
00:33:15,940 --> 00:33:17,070
My mom's in good health.

523
00:33:17,550 --> 00:33:18,000
Don't be like this.

524
00:33:18,050 --> 00:33:18,880
Why are you

525
00:33:18,880 --> 00:33:19,720
so nervous?

526
00:33:19,740 --> 00:33:20,950
I'm not nervous. I'm not.

527
00:33:21,140 --> 00:33:22,400
Any news of your brother?

528
00:33:22,520 --> 00:33:23,200
-No.
-No.

529
00:33:24,960 --> 00:33:25,750
Have you rehearsed?

530
00:33:26,110 --> 00:33:26,720
No, no.

531
00:33:26,750 --> 00:33:27,200
No news, really.

532
00:33:27,240 --> 00:33:27,720
Really.

533
00:33:27,740 --> 00:33:28,180
Nothing.

534
00:33:28,210 --> 00:33:29,410
Let me know if there's news.

535
00:33:29,880 --> 00:33:30,600
As I said,

536
00:33:30,780 --> 00:33:31,910
a cover-up is a crime.

537
00:33:31,950 --> 00:33:32,510
Yes, yes.

538
00:33:33,550 --> 00:33:33,920
Go ahead.

539
00:33:33,950 --> 00:33:34,760
Stay for a bit.

540
00:33:34,790 --> 00:33:35,200
No thanks.

541
00:33:35,480 --> 00:33:36,210
Take care!

542
00:33:36,240 --> 00:33:36,550
Okay.

543
00:34:11,780 --> 00:34:12,460
Are you interested?

544
00:34:13,520 --> 00:34:14,280
Here, take one.

545
00:34:14,300 --> 00:34:15,800
Your salary is so high.

546
00:34:16,710 --> 00:34:17,840
Well, we're short-staffed.

547
00:34:17,840 --> 00:34:18,590
No one would come

548
00:34:18,590 --> 00:34:19,590
for a low salary.

549
00:34:22,429 --> 00:34:23,350
W-What if

550
00:34:23,750 --> 00:34:25,060
I don't have an ID card?

551
00:34:25,800 --> 00:34:26,469
No ID card?

552
00:34:27,480 --> 00:34:27,920
It's okay.

553
00:34:28,100 --> 00:34:29,429
As long as you pass the interview,

554
00:34:30,100 --> 00:34:31,080
specialized personnel

555
00:34:31,110 --> 00:34:32,000
will take care of that.

556
00:34:32,320 --> 00:34:32,750
It's nothing.

557
00:34:33,250 --> 00:34:34,679
Where is it? There's no address.

558
00:34:35,550 --> 00:34:37,150
We had no space to include it.

559
00:34:37,360 --> 00:34:38,360
Call this number.

560
00:34:38,580 --> 00:34:39,190
The recruiter

561
00:34:39,190 --> 00:34:40,280
