562
00:34:40,420 --> 00:34:41,520
What do you do?

563
00:34:42,030 --> 00:34:42,760
We do gifts.

564
00:34:42,960 --> 00:34:43,440
It's on there.

565
00:34:43,440 --> 00:34:44,110
A gift company.

566
00:34:45,520 --> 00:34:46,000
Okay.

567
00:34:46,340 --> 00:34:47,420
Got it. Thank you.

568
00:34:48,580 --> 00:34:49,230
Are you interested?

569
00:34:50,239 --> 00:34:51,070
I'll think about it.

570
00:34:51,670 --> 00:34:52,670
Think about what?

571
00:34:52,710 --> 00:34:53,800
There are very few spots.

572
00:34:54,070 --> 00:34:55,190
A rare opportunity.

573
00:34:57,030 --> 00:34:58,360
It's rare to get paid this much now.

574
00:35:00,200 --> 00:35:01,680
What if I don't pass the interview?

575
00:35:01,710 --> 00:35:02,550
Then I'd just be late for

576
00:35:02,570 --> 00:35:03,230
my current job.

577
00:35:03,230 --> 00:35:04,320
I'll be doubly screwed.

578
00:35:05,010 --> 00:35:06,050
What do you do now?

579
00:35:06,940 --> 00:35:07,920
Is the salary better?

580
00:35:09,910 --> 00:35:10,620
How about this?

581
00:35:11,410 --> 00:35:12,440
My company is just ahead.

582
00:35:12,440 --> 00:35:13,960
About ten minutes by car.

583
00:35:14,600 --> 00:35:15,810
I'll send you there now

584
00:35:15,970 --> 00:35:16,640
for an interview.

585
00:35:17,000 --> 00:35:17,880
Even if you fail,

586
00:35:17,880 --> 00:35:18,560
I'll drive you back.

587
00:35:18,810 --> 00:35:19,730
Will that do?

588
00:35:22,140 --> 00:35:23,440
Let's go. Don't hesitate.

589
00:35:24,590 --> 00:35:25,440
Okay.

590
00:35:25,930 --> 00:35:26,900
Let's go. Come on.

591
00:35:27,380 --> 00:35:28,010
My car's right ahead.

592
00:35:28,400 --> 00:35:28,920
Super convenient.

593
00:35:31,240 --> 00:35:31,590
Here.

594
00:35:31,610 --> 00:35:32,090
Thank you.

595
00:35:52,740 --> 00:35:54,660
Didn't you say it'd take ten minutes?

596
00:35:55,230 --> 00:35:56,230
