597
00:35:57,300 --> 00:35:57,930
I ran out of gas.

598
00:35:58,150 --> 00:35:59,000
There's a gas station ahead.

599
00:35:59,020 --> 00:35:59,910
It'll take a second.

600
00:36:04,410 --> 00:36:05,440
Where are you from?

601
00:36:07,330 --> 00:36:08,170
Maizhou.

602
00:36:11,480 --> 00:36:12,810
Judging from your accent,

603
00:36:13,340 --> 00:36:14,440
